Place one pie crust in a baking dish. Combine spices with LUCKY LEAF Apple Pie Filling. Pour apple mixture into crust. Melt caramels and milk in microwave-safe bowl for about a minute, stirring twice. Pour melted caramels over the LUCKY LEAF Apple Pie Filling. Place pecans on top and cover with the second crust. Vent crust for baking. Brush top of pie crust with the beaten egg wash and sprinkle with 1 teaspoon sugar. Bake at 425 degrees for 45 minutes.